= Carlo Mierendorff

Carlo Mierendorff is the founder of the neo-revisionist ideological tendency, and supports both democratic reforms and extra-parliamentary action to combat the SCPs and authoritarian parties. He is from a middle-class, academic background, and is one of our youngest leaders.

